
# ğŸŸ£ MiniUTXO-Blockchain
*A modular and lightweight Python implementation of a mini UTXO-based blockchain.*

---

## ğŸš€ Overview
This project implements a **miniature blockchain engine** focused on the UTXO (Unspent Transaction Output) model â€” the same conceptual foundation used by Bitcoin.
It includes digital signature flows, UTXO selection, block creation, verification logic, and a clean separation between Wallet, Transaction, Block, and Bank (Ledger).

The goal of the project is to demonstrate how value moves securely in a blockchain system, how ownership is proven, and how transactions are validated using cryptography.

